---
import EventLayout from "../../components/EventLayout.astro";

const images = [
  { src: "/signal-ii/1.png", alt: "SIGNAL II" },
  { src: "/signal-ii/2.jpg", alt: "SIGNAL II" },
  { src: "/signal-ii/3.jpg", alt: "SIGNAL II" },
  { src: "/signal-ii/5.jpg", alt: "SIGNAL II" },
  { src: "/signal-ii/7.jpeg", alt: "SIGNAL II" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="SIGNAL II"
  date="August 21, 2025"
  location="Antwerp, Belgium"
  type="Meetup"
  description="Full house at The Beacon with 61 attendees - two speakers, important questions, and a discussion that kept going long after the talks ended."
  images={images}
>
  <p>The second SIGNAL packed The Beacon to capacity. Francis Wyffels, AI and Robotics professor at Ghent University, asked the question on every roboticist's mind: if ChatGPT can think, what's left for robotic labs to do? He shared how his lab and Dwengo vzw are advancing the local robotics and AI scene.</p>
  <p>Jerome Leclanche, CEO of Ingram Technologies and serial tech entrepreneur with 23 years in the field, followed with a deep dive into hardening AI coding agents - drawing from his background in software engineering, data analytics, and cybersecurity.</p>
  <p>Important questions were asked, predictions were made, and a discussion was started that carried well into the evening.</p>
</EventLayout>
